# Reflection Mode Visual Map

This visual map outlines the systematic approach to reviewing and reflecting on implementations in the AgenticFleet project.

## Reflection Workflow Overview

<mermaid>
graph TD
    Start["🚀 START REFLECTION MODE"] --> ReviewImpl["📚 Review Implementation<br>Results"]
    ReviewImpl --> CheckCompletion{"✓ Implementation<br>Complete?"}
    
    CheckCompletion -->|"No"| ReturnImpl["⏪ Return to<br>Implementation Mode"]
    
    CheckCompletion -->|"Yes"| BeginReview["🔍 Begin<br>Reflection Process"]
    
    BeginReview --> CheckLevel{"📊 Consider<br>Implementation<br>Complexity Level"}
    
    %% Level 1 Reflection
    CheckLevel -->|"Level 1<br>Quick Fix"| L1["🔧 Level 1:<br>Simple Review"]
    L1 --> L1Code["👁️ Review<br>Code Changes"]
    L1Code --> L1Test["✅ Verify<br>Tests Pass"]
    L1Test --> L1Doc["📝 Review<br>Documentation"]
    
    %% Level 2 Reflection
    CheckLevel -->|"Level 2<br>Feature Enhancement"| L2["🛠️ Level 2:<br>Feature Review"]
    L2 --> L2Code["👁️ Review<br>Code Quality"]
    L2Code --> L2Test["✅ Verify<br>Test Coverage"]
    L2Test --> L2Func["🧪 Verify<br>Functionality"]
    L2Func --> L2Doc["📝 Review<br>Documentation"]
    
    %% Level 3 Reflection
    CheckLevel -->|"Level 3<br>Component Development"| L3["🏗️ Level 3:<br>Component Review"]
    L3 --> L3Code["👁️ Review<br>Implementation Quality"]
    L3Code --> L3Test["✅ Verify<br>Test Coverage"]
    L3Test --> L3Integ["🔄 Verify<br>Integrations"]
    L3Integ --> L3Perf["⚡ Check<br>Performance"]
    L3Perf --> L3Doc["📝 Review<br>Documentation"]
    
    %% Level 4 Reflection
    CheckLevel -->|"Level 4<br>System Architecture"| L4["🏢 Level 4:<br>System Review"]
    L4 --> L4Code["👁️ Review<br>Architecture Quality"]
    L4Code --> L4Test["✅ Verify<br>Test Coverage"]
    L4Test --> L4Integ["🔄 Verify<br>System Integrations"]
    L4Integ --> L4Perf["⚡ Check<br>Performance"]
    L4Perf --> L4Sec["🔒 Review<br>Security"]
    L4Sec --> L4Doc["📝 Review<br>Documentation"]
    
    %% Final Steps for All Levels
    L1Doc & L2Doc & L3Doc & L4Doc --> IdentifyImprovements["💡 Identify<br>Improvements"]
    IdentifyImprovements --> CaptureFindings["📋 Capture<br>Findings"]
    CaptureFindings --> NextSteps["🧭 Determine<br>Next Steps"]
    
    %% Decision Point
    NextSteps --> NeedsImprovements{"🤔 Needs<br>Improvements?"}
    
    NeedsImprovements -->|"Yes<br>Major"| PlanNew["📝 Create New<br>Implementation Task"]
    NeedsImprovements -->|"Yes<br>Minor"| QuickFix["🔧 Implement<br>Quick Fixes"]
    NeedsImprovements -->|"No"| FinalizeTask["✅ Finalize<br>Task"]
    
    PlanNew --> PlanMode["⏭️ TRANSITION TO<br>PLANNING MODE"]
    QuickFix --> Verify["✓ Verify<br>Fixes"]
    Verify --> FinalizeTask
    
    FinalizeTask --> UpdateStatus["📊 Update Task<br>Status"]
    UpdateStatus --> Commit["💾 Commit Final<br>Changes"]
    Commit --> NextMode["⏭️ TRANSITION TO<br>PLANNING MODE<br>FOR NEXT TASK"]
    
